    {
        "url": "/quotes/glenn_hoddle_448758",
        "quote": "I run an academy in Spain for young footballers who are released by their clubs and who, in my opinion, deserve a second chance. It is a rewarding job for me, but one that also reveals many of the faults in the English game.",
