    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/glenn_hoddle_448763",
        "quote": "It was my proudest moment as a manager when England drew 0-0 with Italy in Rome to qualify for the World Cup finals. Fifteen years later, the stakes are equally high for both countries as they go head-to-head for a semi-final place at the European Championship.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Glenn Hoddle",
            "url": "/quotes/glenn_hoddle_448763"
        },
