            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/glenn_hoddle_448764",
        "quote": "I often felt as a player in a 4-4-2, you end up being outnumbered in midfield and chasing the ball, so as a manager I liked wingbacks to push forward; it gives the midfield player on the ball three or four options.",
