    {
        "url": "/quotes/glenn_hoddle_448766",
        "quote": "I started the 1998 World Cup with Teddy Sheringham up front but always planned for Michael Owen to face Colombia in our final group game because they defended square and a quick striker would be able to exploit the space behind them.",
